snippet.title: Battletoads / Double Dragon - Versions Comparison (HD)
snippet.description:
Comparison video of Battletoads / Double Dragon (Rare 1993), which features gameplay of the following versions:

Nintendo Entertainment System / NES (0:00)
Game Boy (4:02)
Sega Genesis / Mega Drive (8:17)
Super Nintendo / SNES (12:09)

Which one did you play? Which one do you think is the best version?

If you liked the video, subscribe to my channel and click the bell icon to get new updates.
